&lt;p&gt;AVIS is recognized as world leader in car rental business, owning more than 4000 offices in more than 170 countries around the world and renting more than 500 thousand cars. By making its services accessible throughout the country, AVIS has became a nation-wide company with ten branch offices and around fifty sellers. The company rents more than 300 vehicles in sixteen classes &ndash; from small, economy to luxury vehicles and it is at your disposal 365 days in a year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CLASS UPGRADE:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When you pay with Diners Club card, in case of interest you are eligible for car class upgrade at no additional cost &amp;#8211; e.g. renting a better car then the ordered one at the same price and furthermore you receive a 15% discount. This special offer is applicable only on car rentals through AVIS Slovakia.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;BIRTHDAY-GIFT&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;During the month in which you have birthday Diners Club and AVIS prepared a special birthday gift for you. You have to pay only every second day of your rental period. In combination with the 15% discount you will get total discount of up to 58% off the rental list prices. * Number of days is limited to a maximum of 10 consecutive days.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This offer is valid for Diners Club cardmembers&nbsp;only. For bookings please quote the reference code &lt;strong&gt;AWD X963301&lt;/strong&gt; and inform the staff that you have a Diners Club Card.&lt;/p&gt;

